snippet.title: Khabardar: Options Available To India To Take Retaliatory Action On The Uri Attacks

localized.description:
Emotions of widows, mothers, daughters of those who died in the Uri attacks have been surging all across the nation and demanding answers from the government that how long will the soldiers keep getting martyred.
